<!-- ============================================================
  COVERAGE (覆盖范围对比)
  ============================================================ -->
<section class="section coverage-section" id="coverage" aria-label="覆盖范围说明">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-title reveal">
      <span class="label-chip">覆盖范围</span>
      <p class="t-h2">OSHC 覆盖什么，不覆盖什么？</p>
      <p class="t-body">官方强制最低覆盖要求 + 各档附加项说明，买前务必看清</p>
    </div>
    <div class="coverage-grid">
      <!-- Covered -->
      <div class="coverage-card reveal reveal-delay-1" style="border-color:rgba(14,124,134,.2);">
        <div class="coverage-icon-wrap" style="background:var(--c-primary-pale);" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
            <path d="M12 2L3 7v5c0 5.25 3.75 10.15 9 11.25C17.25 22.15 21 17.25 21 12V7L12 2z" fill="var(--c-primary)"/>
            <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="coverage-title">强制覆盖项（所有保险商必含）</div>
        <div class="coverage-desc">住院及手术费用、急诊就医及救护车、门诊/全科医生诊金（Medicare 不覆盖的部分）、部分精神健康服务、妊娠及分娩（特定情况）</div>
        <span class="coverage-tag" style="background:var(--c-primary-pale);color:var(--c-primary);">✓ 澳移局强制标准</span>
      </div>
      <!-- Optional -->
      <div class="coverage-card reveal reveal-delay-2" style="border-color:rgba(242,120,92,.2);">
        <div class="coverage-icon-wrap" style="background:var(--c-accent-light);" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9" stroke="var(--c-accent)" stroke-width="2"/>
            <path d="M12 7v5l3 3" stroke="var(--c-accent)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="coverage-title">常见附加险（升级档才含）</div>
        <div class="coverage-desc">牙科（洗牙/补牙/拔牙）、配镜及隐形眼镜、物理治疗及脊椎治疗、心理咨询及心理治疗（高次数）、急症回国机票</div>
        <span class="coverage-tag" style="background:var(--c-accent-light);color:var(--c-accent-dark);">◑ 按档位差异</span>
      </div>
      <!-- Not covered -->
      <div class="coverage-card reveal reveal-delay-3" style="border-color:rgba(200,50,50,.1);">
        <div class="coverage-icon-wrap" style="background:#FFF5F5;" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9" stroke="#C83232" stroke-width="2"/>
            <path d="M8 8l8 8M16 8l-8 8" stroke="#C83232" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="coverage-title">通常不覆盖（务必留意）</div>
        <div class="coverage-desc">既有病症（购买前已存在）、美容整形手术、健身/营养补充品、非处方药（日常OTC药）、牙齿矫正（orthodontics）</div>
        <span class="coverage-tag" style="background:#FFF5F5;color:#C83232;">✗ 标准条款不含</span>
      </div>
      <!-- Family -->
      <div class="coverage-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="coverage-icon-wrap" style="background:#F0FDF4;" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
            <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2" stroke="#16A34A" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4" stroke="#16A34A" stroke-width="2"/>
            <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75" stroke="#16A34A" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="coverage-title">家庭保单（带家属留学）</div>
        <div class="coverage-desc">配偶及未满 18 岁子女可加入同一保单，各家保险商家庭档价格差异较大（差距可超 $400/年）。建议单独报价对比，不要直接叠加单人价格。</div>
        <span class="coverage-tag" style="background:#F0FDF4;color:#16A34A;">家庭档单独比价</span>
      </div>
      <!-- Claim -->
      <div class="coverage-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="coverage-icon-wrap" style="background:#EFF6FF;" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
            <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" stroke="#2563EB" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="coverage-title">理赔流程提示</div>
        <div class="coverage-desc">大部分医院（特约网络）可直接刷保险卡结算，无需垫付。非网络医院需先垫付，保留收据后线上申请报销，通常 48-72 小时到账。</div>
        <span class="coverage-tag" style="background:#EFF6FF;color:#2563EB;">网络内医院直付</span>
      </div>
      <!-- Waiting period -->
      <div class="coverage-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="coverage-icon-wrap" style="background:#FFFBEB;" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9" stroke="#D97706" stroke-width="2"/>
            <path d="M12 7v5l3 3" stroke="#D97706" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="coverage-title">等待期须知</div>
